Proficient in Python, PyTorch, TensorFlow, Scikit-learn, and OpenCV. Possesses strong capabilities in Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Natural Language Processing, Computer Vision, and Reinforcement Learning. Additional skills include Data Structures & Algorithms, SQL, Git, and Transformer architectures.

